#: ui/MainWindow.glade:975
msgid "translator-credits"
msgstr "Mauna Linux <dev@maunalinux.top>"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1013
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Dien in"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1039
msgid ""
"The information shared will only be used for hardware compatibility "
"statistics and to be able to troubleshoot compatibility issues in advance.\n"
"\n"
"No personal data is collected.\n"
"\n"
"Hardware information is not shared with third parties and is only sent once "
"during this process."
msgstr ""
"Die inligting wat gedeel word, sal slegs gebruik word vir hardeware-"
"versoenbaarheidsstatistieke en om versoenbaarheidsprobleme vooraf op te "
"los.\n"
"\n"
"Geen persoonlike data word ingesamel nie.\n"
"\n"
"Hardeware-inligting word nie met derde partye gedeel nie en word slegs een "
"keer tydens hierdie proses gestuur."

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1068
msgid "Below is the data which will be sent:"
msgstr "Hieronder is die data wat gestuur sal word:"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1141
msgid "Copy Report"
msgstr "Kopieer Verslag"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1157
msgid "Send"
msgstr "Stuur"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1229
msgid "System Report has been copied to your clipboard!"
msgstr "Stelselverslag is na jou knipbord gekopieer!"

